.TH GENERATE-HELM-CHART 1 "2026-05-22" "SCD Reporting v0.1.0" "SCD Reporting"
.SH NAME
generate-helm-chart \- generate a Helm chart from a Docker Compose file using kompose
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./scripts/generate-helm-chart.sh
[\fB\-f\fR \fIFILE\fR]
[\fB\-o\fR \fIDIR\fR]
[\fB\-n\fR \fINAMESPACE\fR]
[\fB\-r\fR \fIREPLICAS\fR]
[\fB\-\-pvc\-size\fR \fISIZE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B generate-helm-chart.sh
converts a Docker Compose file into a Helm chart using
.BR kompose (1)
and then post-processes the result to correct known deficiencies in
kompose output:
.PP
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
The chart name in
.I Chart.yaml
is set to a clean short name derived from the compose filename rather
than the absolute output path that kompose uses.
.IP \(bu 2
A human-readable
.B description
and
.B appVersion
field are appended.
.RE
.PP
The output directory is always removed and recreated so the chart is
generated from scratch on every run.
.PP
If
.BR helm (1)
is installed,
.B helm lint
is run automatically on the generated chart.
.PP
Note: the generated chart uses kompose's raw output and does not apply
the full Helm templating (values.yaml, helpers, Secret/ConfigMap split)
that the committed charts under
.I helm/
provide.
To regenerate those committed charts, run this script and then apply the
templating by hand, or use it only when you need a quick scaffold from a
new compose file.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-f " FILE"
Compose file to convert.
.br
Default:
.B compose-simple.yaml
.TP
.BI \-o " DIR"
Output directory for the generated chart.
.br
Default:
.BI helm/ CHARTNAME
where
.I CHARTNAME
is derived from the compose filename by stripping the
.B compose-
prefix and file extension.
.TP
.BI \-n " NAMESPACE"
Kubernetes namespace embedded in generated resource manifests.
.br
Default:
.B scd-reporting
.TP
.BI \-r " REPLICAS"
Number of replicas to set in generated Deployment manifests.
.br
Default:
.B 1
.TP
.BI \-\-pvc\-size " SIZE"
Storage request size used for all generated PersistentVolumeClaims.
.br
Default:
.B 1Gi
.TP
.B \-h
Display usage information and exit.
.SH DEPENDENCIES
.TP
.BR kompose (1)
Required.
Install with:
.B brew install kompose
.TP
.BR helm (1)
Optional.
If present,
.B helm lint
is run on the output.
Install with:
.B brew install helm
.SH EXAMPLES
Generate the chart for the simple compose file (default):
.PP
.RS
.EX
./scripts/generate-helm-chart.sh
.EE
.RE
.PP
Generate the chart for the full compose file:
.PP
.RS
.EX
./scripts/generate-helm-chart.sh -f compose.yaml
.EE
.RE
.PP
Generate to a custom directory with larger PVCs:
.PP
.RS
.EX
./scripts/generate-helm-chart.sh -f compose.yaml -o /tmp/my-chart --pvc-size 20Gi
.EE
.RE
.SH FILES
.TP
.I helm/simple/
Templated Helm chart for the simple (SQLite, no Caddy) configuration.
.TP
.I helm/compose/
Templated Helm chart for the full stack (PostgreSQL + Caddy).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kompose (1),
.BR helm (1),
.BR build-docker (1)
